A tool used to securely generate one or more Bitcoin addresses for offline use or for secure offline storage.

The address and private key pair generated allow bitcoins to be received and then spent without running any software or using any external [[eWallet]] service.

The all-in-one web page can be used offline (i.e., without being connected to the Internet).

